                <h1 class="domdom">20</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/420">Barakat! (Algeria) (2006)</a></h1>

                <h2>20 Sep 2009, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>Set in war–torn Algeria in the 1990s, Barakat! (Enough!) follows two women on the dangerous search for the younger woman's husband, a journalist whose writings resulted in his disappearance.</p>

